longBusinessSummary: MAN SE operates in commercial vehicle industry in Germany and internationally. It operates through two divisions, MAN Truck & Bus and MAN Latin America. The MAN Truck & Bus division manufactures commercial vehicles. This division provides vans, trucks, buses, and diesel and gas engines, as well as passenger and freight transportation services. The MAN Latin America division manufactures and sells trucks and buses primarily under the Volkswagen CaminhÃµes e Ãnibus brand. The company was founded in 1758 and is headquartered in Munich, Germany. MAN SE operates as a subsidiary of Traton SE.
